{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0ad56e10e8","title":"对集宁军分区三反斗争情况报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ebeaba6a89","index":0,"year":1952,"month":1,"day":14,"articleId":"0ad56e10e8"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"992675079b","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"0ad56e10e8","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中国人民解放军集宁军分区1952年1月9日关于三反情况的报告谈到，军分区召开了排以上干部会议，由司令员代表分区及个人作检讨和启发报告，发动大家进行揭发批评。会上着重揭露和批评了分区领导利用职权，擅自开支，造成铺张浪费，以及存在严重官像主义的问题。"}],"contents":[{"id":"173f382696","type":"title","text":"对集宁军分区三反斗争情况报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"0ad56e10e8"},{"id":"992675079b","type":"paragraph","text":"各大军区，志愿军，并转各级军区和各军：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"0ad56e10e8"},{"id":"682f784c7e","type":"paragraph","text":"我们愿意看见各级军区和各军有像集宁分区这样的检计，不愿意看那些好像太平无事的报告。集宁分区只说了浪费和生活腐化，还没有提到贪污事件。像一个军分区一定有大批的贪污犯，望各地严格注意。一切没有切实暴露问题和解决问题的机关和部队，必须从头做过，做好了三反再做整编，三反一天没有做好即一天不进行整编。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"0ad56e10e8"},{"id":"212128d3cf","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"0ad56e10e8"},{"id":"53a273ab60","type":"paragraph","text":"一月十四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"0ad56e10e8"}],"page":{"id":"b914cbf69e","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"0ad56e10e8","start":265,"end":265}}}},"__N_SSG":true}